    "display_name": "Write a School Event Ad",
    "long_instructions": "## Write a School Event Ad\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Before You Start:**\r\n\r\nMake sure you have filled in the **K** and **W** columns of your KWL chart for this task.\r\n\r\n**Do:** \r\n\r\nAsk AI to write a short ad for an upcoming school event (like a concert, game, or fundraiser).\r\n\r\n**Try:**\r\n\r\nTest how the ad changes if you give just the name of the event vs. more details like time, location, and who’s invited.\r\n\r\n**Check:**\r\n\r\nDoes it sound clear, exciting, and appropriate for your audience?\r\n\r\n**After You Try It:**\r\n\r\n1. Fill in the **L** column of your KWL chart\r\n2. Press **Continue** to return to the task menu\r\n",
